---
applyTo: '**'
description: Persistence standards
alwaysApply: true
---

Use ProfileStore.

Never save on every change.

Use:

- Session cache
- Autosave
- PlayerRemoving
- BindToClose

Persist only through services.

Controllers must never access datastore.

Create repositories for persistence.

Example:

PlayerDataRepository
InventoryRepository
QuestRepository